{
  "script_id": "magic-square",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42480,
      "text": "相传大禹治水时，一只神龟从洛水浮出，背上刻着一幅奇异的数字图案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "古人称它为洛书，也就是最早的三阶幻方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "这个方阵里，无论横着加、竖着加、还是斜着加，得数都一样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "build-1",
      "filename": "build-build-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/build-build-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "奇数阶幻方有一个优雅的填法，叫暹罗法，又叫楼梯法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "build-2",
      "filename": "build-build-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/build-build-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "把 1 放在第一行正中央，然后每次朝右上方斜着走一格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "build-3",
      "filename": "build-build-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/build-build-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.81,
      "size": 44928,
      "text": "走出边界就从对边绕回来；如果目标格已经有数，就改放到当前格的正下方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "verify-1",
      "filename": "verify-verify-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/verify-verify-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25200,
      "text": "填完之后，我们来验证：把任意一行加起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "verify-2",
      "filename": "verify-verify-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/verify-verify-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "再把任意一列、两条对角线加起来，得数完全相同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "verify-3",
      "filename": "verify-verify-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/verify-verify-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.42,
      "size": 22752,
      "text": "这个所有线共有的和，就叫做幻常数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "property",
      "line_id": "prop-1",
      "filename": "property-prop-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/property-prop-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.58,
      "size": 41328,
      "text": "幻常数其实可以直接算出来，公式是 n 乘以 n 平方加一，再除以二。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "property",
      "line_id": "prop-2",
      "filename": "property-prop-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/property-prop-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "三阶幻方的幻常数是十五，五阶是六十五，七阶是一百七十五。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "切换三阶、五阶、七阶，看暹罗法怎样铺满整个方阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.28,
      "size": 36432,
      "text": "再点亮不同的行、列或对角线，它们的和始终等于幻常数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "幻方用一条简单规则，让行列对角的和奇迹般地相等。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "从洛书到暹罗法，数字里藏着人类对秩序的痴迷。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "magic-square",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/magic-square/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "愿你也能在方格间发现属于自己的规律，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 33.75000000000001,
